 & =\frac{m(\omega_{2}-\omega_{1})^{2}\sqrt{2\pi}}{4(\omega_{1}+\omega_{2})\left(\frac{1}{b^{2}}+\frac{1}{b_{3}^{2}}\right)^{3/2}}\numberthis
