 & =\frac{1}{\omega_{1}^{1/2}\omega_{2}^{1/2}}\frac{8\omega_{1}\omega_{2}+(\omega_{1}-\omega_{2})^{2}}{4\left(\omega_{1}+\omega_{2}\right)}.\numberthis
